title: Targeted-Capture of H. impetiginosus: CAR-02
design_description: DNA sample of  H. impetiginosus individual was extracted using the Qiagen DNeasy Plant Min kit (Qiagen, DK). DNA sample was used as input for the Capture-Seq (Rapid Genomics LLC, Gainesville, FL, USA) custom targeted sequencing method toward sequence characterization, SNP discovery and genotyping. After library preparation and multiplexing using individual barcodes, single-end sequencing, 1x100 nt, was performed in a single lane of an Illumina Hiseq 2000 instrument.
